    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Photographic prints produced by photographing a two-dimensional work, such as a drawing or painting, or by rephotographing another photograph.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
